n simulation (Katz & White 1993) and the recent\nhigh-resolution Eulerian simulation (Bryan & Norman 1997) produced clusters\nwith temperature profiles similar to or steeper than those observed. Our\nresults thus provide a new constraint for adjusting numerical simulations and,\npotentially, discriminating among models of cluster formation. (ABRIDGED)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Nov 1997 02:10:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 1998 00:38:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-30"}
